    <h1 class="hero-title">Server <span>Rules</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">By connecting to LifeStealz.net you agree to follow these rules. Ignorance is not an excuse.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <div class="notice">
      <span class="notice-icon">⚠️</span>
      <p class="notice-text">
        These rules apply to <strong>all LifeStealz platforms</strong> — in-game, Discord, and our store. Staff have final say on all punishment decisions. To appeal, join our Discord at <a href="https://discord.gg/LifeStealz" target="_blank" rel="noopener">discord.gg/LifeStealz</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- SERVER RULES -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-icon">⚔️</span>
        <span class="section-title">Server Rules</span>
      </div>
      <div class="section-body">

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">1</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Hacked Clients <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Using any hacked, cracked, or modified client that provides an unfair advantage is strictly prohibited. This includes but is not limited to kill aura, reach, speed, and fly hacks.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">2</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Movement Mods <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Mods that alter your movement in any unintended way — such as speed, bhop, fly, or step assist — are not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">3</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Inventory Mods <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Mods that automate or assist inventory management in a way that is not achievable in vanilla Minecraft are not permitted.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">4</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Health Indicators <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Any mod or client feature that displays the exact health of other players is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">5</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Radar <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Mods that show the position of other players on a minimap or radar beyond normal render distance are prohibited.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">6</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Freecam <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Using freecam or any camera mod that lets you view areas outside your normal perspective to gain an advantage is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">7</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Auto Place / Easy Place <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Mods that automate block placement or make placing blocks significantly easier than vanilla are not permitted.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">8</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Macros or Scripts <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Automating any in-game action through macros, scripts, or hardware devices (e.g. auto-clickers, jitter-click mice set to auto-click) is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">9</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Abusing Bugs <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Exploiting any unintended bug or glitch for personal gain is prohibited. Report bugs to staff or in our Discord — responsible reporting may be rewarded.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">10</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Using Dupe Methods <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Intentionally duplicating items through any method — whether a client-side exploit, server glitch, or external tool — results in a permanent ban and removal of duped items.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">11</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No IRL Trading <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Buying, selling, or trading in-game items, currency, hearts, or accounts for real money outside of our official store is strictly prohibited.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">12</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Invite Rewards Abuse <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Abusing the invite rewards system through fake accounts, alt abuse, or coordinated manipulation is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">13</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Cross-Server Trading <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Trading items or benefits from other servers in exchange for items or advantages on LifeStealz is not permitted.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">14</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Finding or Using the Seed <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Attempting to find or use the server seed to gain knowledge of terrain, structures, or player bases is a permanent ban offence.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">15</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No More Than 5 Accounts <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">You may not use more than 5 accounts across our server. Alt abuse for boosting stats, hearts, or evading punishments will result in all associated accounts being banned.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">16</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Mouse Tweaks / Scrollers <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Third-party software or hardware that automates mouse actions such as drag clicking, scrolling to place, or inventory tweaks is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">17</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Nitro Boost Rewards Abuse <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Abusing the Nitro Boost reward system — for example boosting and then removing the boost to reclaim rewards — is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">18</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Crafting Modifications <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Mods that automate or assist crafting beyond what is available in vanilla Minecraft are not permitted.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">19</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Staff Impersonation <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Pretending to be a staff member — whether through your username, skin, or chat — is not allowed under any circumstances.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">20</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No External Gambling <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Organising or participating in gambling that involves real money or third-party platforms using LifeStealz items or currency is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CHAT RULES -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-icon">💬</span>
        <span class="section-title">Chat Rules</span>
      </div>
      <div class="section-body">

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">1</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Spamming <span class="rule-tag tag-warn">Warn → Mute</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Do not spam chat yourself or encourage / organise others to spam. This includes repeated messages, excessive caps, and character flooding.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">2</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Harassment <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Mute / Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Targeted harassment, bullying, or sustained negative behaviour towards any player is not tolerated.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">3</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Advertising or Promotion <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Advertising other servers, products, or services in any chat is not allowed. This includes unsolicited DMs to players.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">4</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Discrimination or Hate Speech <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Slurs, hate speech, racism, homophobia, or any discriminatory language targeting any group of people will not be tolerated.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">5</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Death Threats or DDoS Threats <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Threatening real-world harm, DDoS attacks, or any form of threat against a player or the server infrastructure is a permanent ban offence.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">6</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Sharing Others' Private Information <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Sharing or attempting to find another player's personal information — including real name, location, or social accounts — without their consent is a permanent ban offence.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">7</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Pretending to be Someone Else <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Impersonating other players, content creators, or staff members in chat is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">8</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Ban Evasion <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Using an alternate account to bypass an active ban will result in all associated accounts being permanently banned.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">9</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Lying to Staff Members <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Deliberately providing false information to staff during an investigation or support situation may result in a punishment independent of the original issue.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">10</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">Report Bugs, Glitches &amp; Cheaters</div>
            <div class="rule-desc">If you encounter a bug, glitch, or suspected cheater, report it in our Discord at <a href="https://discord.gg/LifeStealz" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:#ff8080;">discord.gg/LifeStealz</a>. Do not post accusations publicly in chat.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- VOICE CHAT RULES -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-icon">🎙️</span>
        <span class="section-title">Voice Chat Rules</span>
      </div>
      <div class="section-body">

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">1</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Voice Changers <span class="rule-tag tag-warn">Warn → Mute</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Using voice changers in any server or Discord voice channel is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">2</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Obnoxious or Extremely Loud Noises <span class="rule-tag tag-warn">Warn → Mute</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Earraping, screaming, or intentionally producing loud or disruptive audio in voice channels is not permitted.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">3</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Slurs, Racism, or Homophobia <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Any slurs, racist remarks, or homophobic language in voice chat will result in an immediate and permanent ban from all LifeStealz platforms.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">4</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Toxicity <span class="rule-tag tag-warn">Staff Discretion</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">General toxic behaviour, trash-talking beyond friendly banter, or creating a hostile environment in voice channels will be handled at staff discretion.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">5</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Soundboards <span class="rule-tag tag-warn">Warn → Mute</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Using soundboards or audio injection software in voice channels is not allowed.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">6</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Derogatory Language <span class="rule-tag tag-temp">Mute / Temp Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Language intended to demean, insult, or degrade other players in voice chat — even without a slur — is not tolerated.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- STORE RULES -->
    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-icon">🛒</span>
        <span class="section-title">Store Rules</span>
      </div>
      <div class="section-body">

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">1</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Chargebacks <span class="rule-tag tag-perm">Permanent Ban</span></div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Initiating a chargeback or payment dispute without contacting us first will result in a permanent ban. Reach out in our Discord before disputing any charge.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">2</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">Ranks Are Non-Transferable</div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Purchased ranks, keys, and cosmetics are tied to your account and cannot be transferred to another player under any circumstances.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="rule-item">
          <div class="rule-num">3</div>
          <div class="rule-text">
            <div class="rule-title">No Refunds on Used Items</div>
            <div class="rule-desc">Refunds are not available for items that have already been redeemed. If you have an issue before redeeming, contact us in Discord first and we will do our best to help.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

